comments: Edwards (MIN) places his off-arm against Jackson Jr. (MEM) and releases from the contact.

comments: Replay review of the out-of-bounds call on McDaniels (MIN) pursuant to a coach's challenge is deemed unsuccessful.  The ruling on the floor of out of bounds stands and the Grizzlies retain possession.
